ode-latest就行了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c975cd8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F4KW1YfFgWQnGKUyRib2jRkt6lIKakoWib810icgicbMxm1v3ctMqsv5NgJzgKmXIv2qqp72SyNZWTuGK8Wiap46SCVXKRwuwJEQRBqB02PlyQOKs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整个过程五分钟搞定，然后你就可以在OpenClaw里直接调用Coding Plan的模型了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=75898b02&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F4KW1YfFgWQmRtLnSnMHN0wjzFibkOBJpFSKDSVgG78R1oDeK4mbx7TrcaP3aibd45KaJhm5aiahlHHv62xlSKLtp9x45sBCBFyPgcKuctqo6Hs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再说Cursor。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">配置入口是Ctrl+Shift+J，搜索Models，在Override OpenAI Base URL那里填上同一个地址，API Key填上，模型选astron-code-latest。更简单，两三分钟的事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f59a5b9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F4KW1YfFgWQngWUlyeT7Zlf936QAgggba6VKM6X589yW8ia2epIgSTINqrHjhPqyjzyuhwFmpLBu489oGjKLeVQKOkibHXbO6qnGfqoJ4z4Jibk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Claude Code的配置稍微多两步，需要在~/.claude/settings.json里设置ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN和ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL，但本质上也是改几个环境变量的事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cdd326d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz